comment from the PM, John Howard, speaking in Sydney about the death
of an Australian in the Yemeni hostage crisis. (First Run at 0715
Asia Pacific Late)
------
GUATEMALA: ANNIVERSARY - Guatemalan President Alvaru Arzu marked the
second anniversary of the signing of the accords ending 36 years of
civil war by unveiling a monument on a patio near the National
Palace -  which consists of two brown hands opened toward the sky -
dedicated to peace. (First Expected Run at 0400 Europe Early)
