<TEXT>
	   NEW YORK (AP) _ Poll results among American newspaper and
broadcast outlets for the 1998 Associated Press Female Athlete of
the Year, based on a 3-2-1 point system (first place votes in
parentheses):
Se Ri Pak (19)           156
