<HEADLINE>
Israeli soldier killed by friendly fire in Lebanon
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES throughout with inquiry, funeral; CORRECTS spelling of
general's name &QL; 
 &UR; By SARI BASHI &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

