<HEADLINE>
Freed hostages say Yemeni troops started fatal shootout
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: RECASTS lede and 2nd graf to clarify attribution. Picks up 3rd
graf pvs &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos LON102, 106, ADE101-103 &QL; 
 &UR; By SAM F. GHATTAS &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
